{
  "texts": [
    "In this scenario, domainspecific data, such as chemical biology and cybercrime, are utilized to fine-tune the pre-searched suffix with the content-aware target.",
    "Cross-Model Transfer employs the pre-searched suffix as an initialization when the LLM in CAS differs from the one in FTS.",
    "Self-Transfer applies when FTS and CAS use the same dataset and LLM.",
    "This is detailed in the following Section 3.5.",
    "Leveraging the self-transferability of suffixes and enhance the efficiency of the search process, we propose an interleaved variant of our approach, i-DeGCG."
  ]
}